column5: My Condolences, sorry for your loss
I'm sorry for your loss. You have my sincerest condolences.
Condolences to you and the family, Dan
Sorry for your loss.  We are preparing for that eventuality with our parents soon.  Take care
Sorry for your loss and condolences to you and your family.
Very sad news Dan.  I'm very sorry.  Joey
So sorry for your loss. My condolences to you and your family.
Sorry for your loss   Paul
My condolances to you Dan, thoughts and prayers are sent
Harry Bow  http://www.elliottracingteam.com/

Very sorry to hear this news....thanks for the link.  He sounded like a great man...willing to do anything for his friends and family.  Our thoughts are with you during this difficult time.  Cliff and Carole (Bly)
Very sorry to hear your sad news Dan, condolances from Diane and I.
My condolences!!
Very sorry for your loss Dan.
really sorry about your loss man, my condolences
Another sad moment, hope the memories stay with you
Sorry for your famlies loss.
Condolences to you Dan. He's surely in a better place.
Thank you all for your kindness & support.. I love this place too..Peace . Hold your loved ones tight & let 'em all know your deepest heart.

Wow, can you imagine the racing going on at Heaven's Speedway?  Dale, Alan, Davey, BP, Kenny, Tim & now your step-Dad....maybe he can teach that 'ol Earnhardt a thing or two about qualifying....  My deepest condolances to you Danbo...take it easy.
Aint it the truth........ Our condolences to you and yours Dan..... Peace be with you.
Sorry to hear that, my thoughts are with you and your family.
Deepest condolences Dan.
Sorry for your loss Dan
Sad to hear it Dan.
sorry to hear about your loss!
Thanx again..Hey MuskyBill..I had the same thought myself..
Our condolences!  Cliff & Sue
Sorry to hear Dan, your stepdad sounded like a pretty interesting individual.
our condolences also Dan
Sorry for your loss.
sorry to hear
Sorry for your loss
Very sorry for your loss.  Sincerely, 1leg
